So the top-to-bottom ocean warming of 0.001°C/yr (Egad!) is not ultimately responding to forcing from solar radiation modulated by cloud albedo?

So then where does the 0.001°C/yr whole ocean warming come from? https://t.co/uLLKtKV1QD

